	<Title>
		Photodynamic therapy: An effective treatment for lung cancer?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Photodynamic therapy may play a limited role in lung cancer treatment.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Is photodynamic therapy an effective treatment for lung cancer?
	</Question>
